description:
Both the Rogue and Blondie have faced some of the best
wrestlers US has to offer. Both have shown skill and
determination in those losses. Both have shown a no
quit and never give up attitude. Both wrestlers are
looking for their first win. One will want it more,
one will take it, and one will fuck the shit out of
the loser in a brutal rd4.
title: SUMMER VENGEANCE
